author_ssm: Megan O'Shea and Molly A. Cross
unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Spain Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Spain Serials contains over 50 titles published in and about Spain between 1935 and 2003.  The majority of the serials are about the Spanish Civil War.  The bulk of the collection dates from the 1930s and the 1980s.
